window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A group of bikers known in their city not only as one of the best crews but also as causing havoc wherever they go.</b></p> <p>From illegal street races to owning their businesses, the Zoo Boyz have the world at their fingertips. The decision made by Zu on behalf of the Zoo Boyz puts both his crew and his friendship with Chevy in jeopardy.</p> <p>As the group of five handles different situations, they encounter women they believe will ride for them. When they put trust, lust, and death on the line, it shakes things up within the crew, which makes them question each other. Not only is their friendship put to the test, but so is their loyalty. Some will win and some will lose, but in the end, will there still be a crew called Zoo?</p>"; 
